<br><br>
<p>Shopping when you have food allergies is a daunting experience. You have to constantly check labels to verify that a food is safe 
and even then still worry if you missed something.
</p>
<p>
    Safe Eats is a web application that will allow you to create an account and input an allergen that you are avoiding and the UPC of a food item
    that you are considering and check if it should be safe or if it needs to be avoided.
</p>
<p>Please note, that while every care is taken to ensure that the information is up-to-date, please be sure to double check the ingredients as 
    manufacturer's change their recipes and those changes may not always be updated yet. 
</p>

